subject: Dear Beneficiary,
body:
Dear Beneficiary,
Read carefully!!
This electronic message is confidential and strictly for you. It is obvious that he has not received his fund, which amounts to the sum of $3.8 million, due to corrupt government officials of the past who almost withheld the fund for themselves for selfish reasons and took advantage of his fund, all in an attempt to scam your fund
It has caused so many losses on your part and unnecessary delays in receiving your fund.
The National Central Bureau of Interpol, reinforced by the United Nations and the Federal Bureau of Investigation (F.B.I), has successfully passed a mandate to the current president of the International Monetary Fund to promote the settlement exercise of all foreign debts owed to you and other people who have not. receive the sum of the contract, lottery/betting, inheritance and the like. You will receive your payment using an ATM card.
ATM Card: We will issue you an ATM card with a personalized PIN with your name encrypted that you can use to withdraw up to $10,000 per day from any ATM that has the Visa card logo. Additionally, with the ATM card you can transfer your funds to your bank account. The ATM card comes with a manual or manual to tell you how to use it. Your payment will be sent to you via ATM card and delivered to you via Young Express. As we have signed a contract with Young Express, you will only have to pay 90 Euros.
Please note that anyone who asks you for any kind of money above the usual rate is definitely a scammer and you will need to stop communicating with all other people, if you have been in contact with any, also remember that the only thing they will have to spend is 90 Euros, nothing more! Nothing less! And we guarantee receipt of your fund within 2 business days after receiving payment.
NOTE: Everything has been taken care of by the Federal Government.
including taxes, custom paper and clearance fees for everything you can
You have to pay 90 Euros. This is because Young Express' COD (Cost On Delivery) service does not apply to international shipping.
according to its terms. Please contact Mr. Alex Alozie.
Director's Compensation Fund Department (United Bank ATM VISA CARD) and send him the payment receipt urgently so that everything is completed immediately without further delay.
Contact email: (

Payment amount: only  90 Euros. I want you to send me the MTCN. Once you send the payment upon receiving the payment, the delivery officer will ensure that your package is sent within 45 business hours.
Yours sincerely.
Ms. Kristalina Georgieva
